The '''MK6 missile launcher''' was an infantry weapons system produced by [[Zoltan Arms]]. A standard magazine for the system contained six [[Missile/Legends|missiles]], although the missiles came in anti-personnel and anti-vehicle variants: individual missiles of either type cost 100 and 200 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] respectively, and the launcher system itself cost 800 credits.

